Global constraints
1. Commit prefixes: `edge:`, `ios:`, `cli:`, `shared:`, `docs:`
2. No plaintext secrets — use GitHub or Worker secrets.
3. Tesla API scopes are **read-only**.
4. Every push MUST pass: commitlint · worker.yml · ios-ci.yml · cli.yml · contract-check.yml · docs-automation.yml.
5. Single-file ≤ 150 LOC, helpers go to `/utils`.